Inside recon-ng console, execute:

help
show modules
workspaces create lab9_recon
workspaces select lab9_recon
Step 5: Install Essential Modules
Install reconnaissance modules:

marketplace search
marketplace install recon/domains-hosts/google_site_web
marketplace install recon/hosts-hosts/resolve
marketplace install recon/domains-hosts/hackertarget
marketplace install reporting/html
show modules
Step 6: Perform Basic Reconnaissance
Add target domain and run modules:

db insert domains example.com
modules load recon/domains-hosts/google_site_web
options set SOURCE example.com
run
show hosts
Resolve discovered hosts:

modules load recon/hosts-hosts/resolve
run
show hosts
Generate HTML report:

modules load reporting/html
options set FILENAME ~/lab9_osint/recon_report.html
run
exit
View the report:

firefox ~/lab9_osint/recon_report.html &
