Troubleshooting Tips
Issue: recon-ng modules not found

Solution: Run marketplace refresh then reinstall modules
Issue: Python script permission denied

Solution: Ensure script is executable: chmod +x script.py
Issue: recon-ng command not found

Solution: Install recon-ng: sudo apt update && sudo apt install recon-ng -y
Issue: Empty results from recon-ng

Solution: Some modules require API keys. Use modules that work without keys for this lab
Issue: Timeout errors in automation

Solution: Increase timeout value in subprocess.run() or reduce number of modules
